            Denise A. Piechnik, PhD
          
          
            
              Raised on a farm in mid-Michigan, I found my passion
              for science in California doing ecological research. Now
              residing in NY, I am an aspiring data scientist and fiddle
              player.
              I recently left an academic position to change careers
              to apply my skills to conservation and sustainability
              problem-solving.
